* Select shipping method: If enabled, cart contents will be hidden after clicking on the Google Checkout button in the shopping cart, and restored if "Edit Cart" link was activated.
* Select delivery method: If enabled, basket contents will be hidden after clicking on the Google Checkout button in the shopping basket, and restored if "Edit Basket" link was activated.

* Select shipping method: You will be redirected to GoogleCheckout in a few seconds.
* Select delivery method: You will be redirected to Google Checkout in a few seconds.
